data.description: Home has been completely remodeled including new windows and HVAC.    Welcome to your dream retreat in Blairsville, Georgia! This stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bath cabin is nestled  in the picturesque surroundings and is ideally situated close to the serene Lake Nottely. Step into a world  of rustic elegance as this home has been completely remodeled, boasting exquisite features and modern  amenities throughout. As you enter, you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting atmosphere created by  the luxurious vinyl plank (LVP) floors that run seamlessly throughout the cabin. The spacious living area  is adorned with captivating barnwood accent walls, adding a touch of rustic charm and creating a cozy  ambiance for relaxing evenings. The heart of the home is the gorgeous kitchen, showcasing beautiful  granite countertops that perfectly complement the cabin's aesthetic. This well-appointed culinary haven  is equipped with high-quality appliances, ensuring that your cooking experiences are both convenient  and enjoyable. Outside, you'll discover a world of natural beauty and tranquility. The cabin's location near  Lake Nottely provides easy access to a wealth of outdoor activities, including boating, fishing, and  swimming and all the North Georgia Mountains have to offer. Spend your days exploring the serene  waters or simply basking in the breathtaking scenery.    This remarkable cabin comes with all appliances included, ensuring a seamless move-in experience.  Whether you're seeking a permanent residence, a vacation getaway, or an investment opportunity, this  cabin offers it all.    Don't miss the chance to make this exquisite cabin your own. Embrace the tranquility of Blairsville,  Georgia, and create lifelong memories in this beautifully remodeled retreat. Schedule a showing today  and unlock the door to your dream home.    **$1,500 in lender incentives if preferred lender is used. **
